Class ProjectDao

java.lang.Object
aor.fpbackend.dao.AbstractDao<ProjectEntity>
aor.fpbackend.dao.ProjectDao
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ProjectDao extends AbstractDao<ProjectEntity>
ProjectDao class provides data access operations for ProjectEntity.

This class implements methods to perform CRUD operations and custom queries related to projects in the database. It extends the AbstractDao class to inherit generic data access operations and adds specific methods for project management.
